<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />过圣诞节的话，<delay8 />
肯定少不了交换礼物呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一边在心里想着对方，
一边挑选礼物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得这是很幸福的时光。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每年一到12月的这个时候，<delay8 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就会回想起那一年的圣诞节<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对不起，<delay20 />是我自己的一点私事。<pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
这个平安夜，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你和我交换礼物吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想用<delay8 />快乐的经历
覆盖掉过去的记忆。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请你把礼物<delay8 />包装好哦。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />广场上摆出了圣诞树，<delay8 />
圣诞节的氛围高涨起来了～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />树上的装饰品也很可爱，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定是<colour id="3" />西施惠<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />
出谋划策的吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>